username=professor&password=prof123&grant_type=password

### List turmas (use token from previous response)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/turmas
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create turma
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/turmas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "nome": "1A",
  "capacidade": 30
}

### List alunos (filters)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/alunos?search=a&status=ativo&sort=nome
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

